ipotle.ca/rewards-terms" data-testid="link-with-safety" data-renderer-mark="true">Rewards Terms</a> and, <a class="css-1rn59kg" title="https://www.chipotle.ca/terms-of-use" href="https://www.chipotle.ca/terms-of-use" data-testid="link-with-safety" data-renderer-mark="true">Terms of Use</a>.</p><p data-renderer-start-pos="1006">*By enrolling in Chipotle Rewards, you confirm you are a resident of Canada (excluding Quebec), at least 16 years old, have parent/legal guardian consent if you are not age of majority, and you agree to&nbsp;<a class="css-1rn59kg" title="https://www.chipotle.ca/about-us/privacy-notice" href="https://www.chipotle.ca/about-us/privacy-notice" data-testid="link-with-safety" data-renderer-mark="true"><u data-renderer-mark="true">Chipotle’s Privacy Policy</u></a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a class="css-1rn59kg" title="https://www.chipotle.ca/about-us/rewards-terms" href="https://www.chipotle.ca/about-us/rewards-terms" data-testid="link-with-safety" data-renderer-mark="true"><u data-renderer-mark="true">Chipotle Rewards Terms and Conditions</u></a>.&nbsp;</p><p data-renderer-start-pos="1280">**By selecting “yes”, you agree to receive email messages about Chipotle offers and promotions. You can unsubscribe at any time. Your consent is not required to make a purchase or enroll in Chipotle Rewards. To unsubscribe from emails, use the link in each email or visit Personal &amp; Preferences in the Account section and deselect your email subscription.</p><p data-renderer-start-pos="1637">If you sign up for SMS offers and promotions, you acknowledge that Chipotle Mexican Grill Canada Corp or its designated agent may send you commercial text messages using an auto-dialer or other technology. You consent to that type of contact. Standard message and data rates may apply. You can opt out at any time. You are not required to agree to this as a condition of Purchasing any property, goods, or services. Text HELP for help. Text STOP to cancel. Visit the Mobile Terms &amp; Conditions section of our Terms of Use to learn more.</p><p data-renderer-start-pos="2174">Chipotle Mexican Grill Canada Corp., 900-1959 Upper Water St., Halifax NS B3J 2X2 Canada, <a class="css-1rn59kg" title="https://www.chipotle.ca" href="https://www.chipotle.ca/" data-testid="link-with-safety" data-renderer-mark="true">www.chipotle.ca</a>&nbsp;</p>\n',createAnAccount2sv:"<p>Message and data rates may apply.</p>\n",signIn:'<p>By signing in, I agree to <a href="https://www.chipotle.ca/privacy-policy" title="https://www.chipotle.ca/privacy-policy">Chipotle\'s Privacy Policy</a>, <a href="https://www.chipotle.ca/terms-of-use" title="https://www.chipotle.ca/terms-of-use">Terms of Use</a>, and if you are a member of our Rewards program, the <a href="https://www.chipotle.ca/rewards-terms" title="https://www.chipotle.ca/rewards-terms">Rewards Terms</a>, and to receiving account security/verification text messages from Chipotle. Msg &amp; Data rates may apply.</p>\n',updateProfile:"<p>By updating your account, you authorize Chipotle to send a text to the phone number selected with a verification code. Msg &amp; Data rates may apply.</p>\n",personalAndPreference:'<p>By enrolling in Chipotle Rewards and/or participating in the program, you confirm you are a resident of Canada (excluding Quebec), at least 16 years old, have parent/legal guardian consent if you are not age of majority, and you agree to&nbsp;<a href="https://www.chipotle.ca/about-us/privacy-notice">Chipotle’s Privacy Policy</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a href="https://www.chipotle.ca/about-us/rewards-terms">Chipotle Rewards Terms and Conditions</a>.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>By electing to receive email updates, you agree to receive email messages about Chipotle offers and promotions. You can unsubscribe at any time. Your consent is not required to make a purchase or enroll in Chipotle Rewards. To unsubscribe from emails, use the link in each email or visit Personal &amp; Preferences in the Account section and deselect your email subscription.</p>\n<p>If you elect to receive texts, you will receive recurring automated marketing messages to your mobile number. Standard message and data rates may apply. Text STOP or visit Personal &amp; Preferences in the Account section and deselect your text subscription to unsubscribe from texts. Text HELP for help.</p>\n<p>Chipotle Mexican Grill Canada Corp., 900-1959 Upper Water St., Halifax NS B3J 2X2 Canada,&nbsp;<a href="http://www.chipotle.ca">www.chipotle.ca</a><a>&nbsp;</a></p>\n',loggedInUnEnrolled:'<p>By enrolling in Chipotle Rewards, you confirm you are a resident of Canada (excluding Quebec), at least 16 years old, have parent/legal guardian consent if you are not age of majority, and you agree to&nbsp;<a href="https://www.chipotle.ca/about-us/privacy-notice">Chipotle’s Privacy Policy</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a href="https://www.chipotle.ca/about-us/rewards-terms">Chipotle Rewards Terms and Conditions</a>.&nbsp;</p>\n',retroCredit:"<p>We do not accept credit requests for app or online purchases at this time. You will have up to 30 days after the purchase to receive credit. If your request is approved, your points will show up in your account in 24-48 hours. If your points do not show up after 48 hours, we may not have been able to grant your request. View our Terms &amp; Conditions for a list of reasons why a request may not be granted. You can always contact customer service for help.&nbsp;</p>\n",nutritionCalculatorBuilderDisclaimer:"<p>2,000 calories a day is used for general nutrition advice, but calorie needs vary. Nutritional content may vary because of variations in portion size or recipes, changes in growing seasons, or differences in the sources of our ingredients. We may update this chart from time to time.</p>\n"}:e===J.C_.UK?{createAnAccount:'<p>By creating an account, you assert you are at least 16 years of age and you agree to Chipotle’s <a href="https://www.chipotle.co.uk/privacy-notice">Privacy Policy</a> and <a href="https://www.chipotle.co.uk/terms-of-use">Terms of Use</a>.<br>\n<br>\nBy selecting “Yes”, you agree to receive email messages about Chipotle offers and promotions. You can unsubscribe at any time. Your consent is not required to make a purchase. To unsubscribe from emails, use the link in each email or visit Personal &amp; Preferences in the Account section and deselect your email subscription.<br>\n<br>\nIf you elect to receive texts, you will receive recurring automated marketing messages to your mobile number. Standard message and data rates may apply. Text STOP or visit Personal &amp; Preferences in the Account section and deselect your text subscription to unsubscribe from texts. Text HELP for help.</p>\n',createAnAccountOrderConfirmation:'<p>By creating an account, you assert you are at least 16 years of age and you agree to Chipotle’s&nbsp;<a href="https://www.chipotle.co.uk/privacy-notice">Privacy Policy</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a href="https://www.chipotle.co.uk/terms-of-use">Terms of Use</a>.</p>\n<p>By selecting “Yes”, you agree to receive email messages about Chipotle offers and promotions. You can unsubscribe at any time. Your consent is not required to make a purchase. To unsubscribe from emails, use the link in each email or visit Personal &amp; Preferences in the Account section and deselect your email subscription.</p>\n<p>If you elect to receive texts, you will receive recurring automated marketing messages to your mobile number. Standard message and data rates may apply. Text STOP or visit Personal &amp; Preferences in the Account section and deselect your text subscription to unsubscribe from texts. Text HELP for help.</p>\n',createAnAccount2sv:"<p>Message and data rates may apply.</p>\n",signIn:"",updateProfile:"",personalAndPreference:'<p>Toggle the buttons above in order to receive marketing and other communications (which may include exclusive offers, promotions and discount codes) from Chipotle (or service providers acting on Chipotle’s behalf). You may unsubscribe at any time. Chipotle\'s website and communications are subject to our <a href="https://www.chipotle.co.uk/privacy-notice">Privacy Policy</a> and <a href="https://www.chipotle.co.uk/terms-of-use">Terms of Use</a>.</p>\n',loggedInUnEnrolled:'<p>By joining, I am confirming I am 13 years of age or older, will be enrolled in Chipotle Rewards, will receive email updates, promotions and offers from Chipotle, and agree to&nbsp;<a title="Privacy Policy" href="https://www.chipotle.co.uk/about-us/privacy-policy">Chipotle’s&nbsp;<u>Privacy Policy</u></a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<u><a title="Terms And Conditions" href="https://www.chipotle.co.uk/about-us/rewards-terms">Terms &amp; Conditions</a></u>.</p>\n',retroCredit:'<p>We do not accept credit requests for app or online purchases at this time. You will have up to 30 days after the purchase to receive credit. If your request is approved, your points will show up in your account in 24-48 hours. If your points do not show up after 48 hours, we may not have been able to grant your request. View our&nbsp;<a href="https://www.chipotle.co.uk/about-us/rewards-terms">Terms And Conditions</a>&nbsp;for a list of reasons why a request may not be granted. You can always&nbsp;<a href="https://www.chipotle.co.uk/contact-us#report-an-issue">Contact Customer Service</a>&nbsp;for help.</p>\n',nutritionCalculatorBuilderDisclaimer:'<p>Data is derived by laboratory analysis. Products may be subject to some variation depending on ingredients used, supplier, and seasonality. Because of this, the products used may not be identical to the products served in our restaurants.</p>\n<p>Nutritional data is listed per serving. Adults need around 2000 kcal a day. For all allergen information, please visit <a href="/content/chipotle/gb/en/allergens.html">chipotle.co.uk/allergens</a></p>\n'}:{createAnAccount:'<p data-renderer-start-pos="2511">By creating an account, I agree to <a class="css-1rn59kg" title="https://www.chipotle.com/privacy-policy" href="https://www.chipotle.com/privacy-policy" data-testid="link-with-safety" data-renderer-mark="true">Chipotle\'s Privacy Policy</a>, <a class="css-1rn59kg" title="https://www.chipotle.com/terms-of-use" href="https://www.chipotle.com/terms-of-use" data-testid="link-with-safety" data-renderer-mark="true">Terms of Use</a>, and if you are a member of our Rewards program, the <a class="css-1rn59kg" title="https://www.chipotle.com/rewards-terms" href="https://www.chipotle.com/rewards-terms" data-testid="link-with-safety" data-renderer-mark="true">Rewards Terms</a>, and to receiving account security/verification text messages from Chipotle. Msg &amp; Data rates may apply. I further agree that by creating an account the information I provide, including my personal information, will be used to create and administer my account and as otherwise provided in <a class="css-1rn59kg" title="https://www.chipotle.com/privacy-policy" href="https://www.chipotle.com/privacy-policy" data-testid="link-with-safety" data-renderer-mark="true">Chipotle\'s Privacy Policy</a> (including the <a class="css-1rn59kg" title="https://www.chipotle.com/privacy-policy#financial-incentives" href="https://www.chipotle.com/privacy-policy#financial-incentives" data-testid="link-with-safety" data-renderer-mark="true">Notice of Financial Incentives</a>), <a class="css-1rn59kg" title="https://www.chipotle.com/rewards-terms" href="https://www.chipotle.com/rewards-terms" data-testid="link-with-safety" data-renderer-mark="true">Rewards Terms</a> and, <a class="css-1rn59kg" title="https://www.chipotle.com/terms-of-use" href="https://www.chipotle.com/terms-of-use" data-testid="link-with-safety" data-renderer-mark="true">Terms of Use</a>.</p><p data-renderer-start-pos="2856">*If you sign up for text offers and promotions, you acknowledge that CMG Strategy Co., LLC or its designated agent may send you commercial text messages using an auto-dialer or other technology. You consent to that type of contact. Standard message and data rates may apply. You can opt out at any time. You are not required to agree to this as a condition of purchasing any property, goods, or services. Text HELP for help. Text STOP to cancel. Visit the Mobile Terms &amp; Conditions section of our <a class="css-1rn59kg" title="https://www.chipotle.com/terms-of-use" href="https://www.chipotle.com/terms-of-use" data-testid="link-with-safety" data-renderer-mark="true"><u data-renderer-mark="true">Terms of Use</u></a> to learn more.&nbsp;</p>',createAnAccountOrderConfirmation:'<p data-renderer-start-pos="2511">By creating an account, I agree to <a class="css-1rn59kg" title="https://www.chipotle.com/privacy-policy" href="https://www.chipotle.com/privacy-policy" data-testid="link-with-safety" data-renderer-mark="true">Chipotle\'s Privacy Policy</a>, <a class="css-1rn59kg" title="https://www.chipotle.com/terms-of-use" href="https://www.chipotle.com/terms-of-use" data-testid="link-with-safety" data-renderer-mark="true">Terms of Use</a>, and if you are a member of our Rewards program, the <a class="css-1rn59kg" title="https://www.chipotle.com/rewards-terms" href="https://www.chipotle.com/rewards-terms" data-testid="link-with-safety" data-renderer-mark="true">Rewards Terms</a>, and to receiving account security/verification text messages from Chipotle. Msg &amp; Data rates may apply. I further agree that by creating an account the information I provide, including my personal information, will be used to create and administer my account and as otherwise provided in <a class="css-1rn59kg" title="https://www.chipotle.com/privacy-policy" href="https://www.chipotle.com/privacy-policy" data-testid="link-with-safety" data-renderer-mark="true">Chipotle\'s Privacy Policy</a> (including the <a class="css-1rn59kg" title="https://www.chipotle.com/privacy-policy#financial-incentives" href="https://www.chipotle.com/privacy-policy#financial-incentives" data-testid="link-with-safety" data-renderer-mark="true">Notice of Financial Incentives</a>), <a clas