hipotle Rewards, I am confirming I am 13 years of age or older, will receive email updates, promotions and offers from Chipotle, and agree to&nbsp;<u><a title="Privacy Policy" href="https://www.chipotle.com/about-us/privacy-policy">Chipotle\'s Privacy Policy</a></u>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<u><a title="Rewards Terms And Conditions" href="https://www.chipotle.com/about-us/rewards-terms">Rewards Terms and Conditions</a></u>.</p>\n<p>By opting in to \'Text,\' I agree to receive Chipotle updates and offers via text and agree to&nbsp;<u><a title="Privacy Policy" href="https://www.chipotle.com/about-us/privacy-policy">Chipotle\'s Privacy Policy</a></u>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<u><a title="Terms and Conditions" href="https://www.chipotle.com/about-us/rewards-terms">Terms and Conditions</a></u>.&nbsp;Recurring marketing messages will be sent to your account mobile number using automated technology. Standard msg and data rates may apply. Text STOP to cancel. Text HELP for help. By updating this account, I agree to&nbsp;<u><a title="Privacy Policy" href="https://www.chipotle.com/about-us/privacy-policy">Chipotle\'s Privacy Policy</a></u>&nbsp;&nbsp;and&nbsp;<u><a title="Terms of Use" href="https://www.chipotle.com/about-us/terms-of-use">Terms of Use</a></u>.&nbsp;</p>\n',loggedInUnEnrolled:'<p>By joining, I am confirming I am 13 years of age or older, will be enrolled in Chipotle Rewards, will receive email updates, promotions and offers from Chipotle, and agree to&nbsp;<a title="Privacy Policy" href="https://www.chipotle.com/about-us/privacy-policy">Chipotle’s&nbsp;<u>Privacy Policy</u></a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<u><a title="Terms And Conditions" href="https://www.chipotle.com/about-us/rewards-terms">Terms &amp; Conditions</a></u>.&nbsp;</p>\n',retroCredit:'<p>We do not accept credit requests for app or online purchases at this time. You will have up to 30 days after the purchase to receive credit. If your request is approved, your points will show up in your account in 24-48 hours. If your points do n